  "description": {
    "zh": "我们刚才说到哪了？哦，对了，在海关工业区的某个地方有一栋建筑里有一个绿幕房间。我希望你能找到这个房间并在那里安装一个WI-FI摄像头。\n\n我们需要确保这个地方不会被任何其他人用它来做事。所以在门前安装一个拌雷陷阱，我可以借给你一套，别弄丢了。\n综上所述，祝你好运。",
    "en": "So, where were we again? Oh yeah right, somewhere in the industrial zone theres a building that has a greenscreen in it. I want you to locate this room and install a wi-fi camera there.\n\nWe'll need to assure that this place won't be used by anyone, at least not for it's intended purpose. So plant a grenade trap infront of the door, I can lend you an installation kit, don't mess this up.\nAnyway, good luck out there."
  },
